      "title": "Cleric Talent Tree",
      "category": "Asteria Handbook/Class Talent Trees",
      "source": "Asteria Handbook/Class Talent Trees/Cleric Talent Tree.md",
      "content": "\n## Tier 1 — Foundations of Faith\n\n| Talent | Type | Ranks | Description |\n|------|------|-------|-------------|\n| Divine Rebuke | Active | 5 | Condemn a foe with divine authority, risking backlash on failure. |\n| Sacred Aegis | Reactive | 5 | Shield allies at the moment of impact, converting or negating harm. |\n| Beacon of Hope | Passive | 5 | Steady allies against fear, despair, and morale collapse. |\n| Divine Insight | Passive | 5 | Receive guidance and foresight through divine whispers. |\n| Judgment Brand | Active | 5 | Mark a creature for divine reckoning and conditional punishment. |\n\n---\n\n## Tier 2 — Sustained Faith & Control\n\n| Talent | Type | Ranks | Description |\n|------|------|-------|-------------|\n| Hymn of Restoration | Active | 5 | Sustained healing prayer that escalates over time. |\n| Consecrated Ground | Active | 5 | Sanctify an area to empower allies and weaken enemies. |\n| Sanctuary of Silence | Active | 5 | Suppress divine and magical escalation within an area. |\n| Mana Well | Passive | 5 | Increase mana capacity and recovery through faith discipline. |\n| Blessed Resilience | Passive | 5 | Reduce exhaustion, corruption, and divine backlash effects. |\n\n---\n\n## Tier 3 — Authority & Sacrifice\n\n| Talent | Type | Ranks | Description |\n|------|------|-------|-------------|\n| Burden of Faith | Passive (Escalation) | 5 | Convert divine backlash into controlled consequences. |\n| Echoes of the Faithful | Passive / Narrative | 5 | Gain power from prayers, rituals, and communal belief. |\n| Divine Guardian | Reactive | 5 | Intercept damage and consequences meant for allies. |\n| Hallowed Ground | Active | 5 | Create lingering holy zones that alter encounters and scenes. |\n\n---\n\n## Tier 4 — Divine Covenant\n\n| Talent | Type | Ranks | Description |\n|------|------|-------|-------------|\n| Vowbound Miracle | Active / Narrative | 5 | Swear sacred vows to invoke miracles with lasting consequences. |\n| Fortified Mind | Passive | 5 | Achieve near-absolute mental and spiritual resilience. |\n| Divine Intervention | Active / Narrative | 5 | Call directly upon your deity to alter fate at great cost. |\n\n---"
