      "content": "---\ntags:\n  - Metal\nItem Class: Common\nMaterial Type: Metal\nMaterial Form: Ingot\nSource: Silver Ore\nWeight: 1kg\nWeight Class: Light\nDurability: Moderate\nEnchantment Affinity: 30% (+2 dice)\nMarket Value: 20 Marks\n---\n\n\n## Effect\nSilver Ingots are prized for their ability to channel divine and spiritual energy, making them ideal for enchanted weapons and relics.\n\n---\n\n## Crafting Use\n- Holy weapons\n- Ritual tools\n- Magical components\n\n---\n\n## Material Traits\n- Soft but magically potent  \n- High purity  \n- Reacts to corruption  \n\n---\n\n## Alloy Use\n- Reinforces enchanted weapons  \n\n---\n\n## Enchantment Use\n- Boosts Light and Spirit effects  \n- Increased effectiveness vs undead  \n\n---\n\n## Crafting Source\n- Requires: 4x [[Silver Ore]]\n\n---\n\n## Quote\n*\"Silver reveals what darkness hides.\"*"
