      "source": "Items/Resources & Materials/Ingots/Unusual Ingots/Cobalt Ingot.md",
      "content": "---\ntags:\n  - Metal\nItem Class: Unusual\nMaterial Type: Metal\nMaterial Form: Ingot\nSource: Cobalt Ore\nWeight: 1.3kg\nWeight Class: Medium\nDurability: High\nEnchantment Affinity: 35% (+2 dice)\nDamage Modifier: 2\nArmor Modifier: 2\nMarket Value: 50 Marks\n---\n\n\n## Effect\nCobalt is a mana-reactive metal that amplifies energy flow through weapons and armor. It enhances elemental interactions while maintaining structural stability.\n\n---\n\n## Crafting Use\n- Enchanted weapons\n- Battlemage armor\n- Arcane conduits\n- Magical cores\n\n---\n\n## Material Traits\n- Highly responsive to magical energy  \n- Stable under repeated enchantment use  \n- Naturally cool and conductive  \n- Resistant to arcane corrosion  \n\n---\n\n## Enchantment Use\n- Enhances Lightning and Ice effects  \n- Improves enchantment efficiency  \n- Supports multi-enchantment builds  \n\n---\n\n## Combat Integration\n- +2 Damage Modifier  \n- +2 Armor Modifier  \n- Favours elemental and hybrid builds  \n\n---\n\n## Crafting Source\n- Requires: 4x [[Cobalt Ore]]\n\n---\n\n## Quote\n*\"It does not hold power — it awakens it.\"*"
