      "slug": "gallium",
      "title": "Gallium",
      "category": "Items/Resources & Materials/Ingots/Unusual Ingots",
      "source": "Items/Resources & Materials/Ingots/Unusual Ingots/Gallium.md",
      "content": "---\ntags:\n  - Metal\nItem Class: Unusual\nMaterial Type: Metal\nMaterial Form: Liquid\nWeight Class: Light\nDurability: Very Low\nEnchantment Affinity: 20% (+1 dice)\nMarket Value: 25 Marks\n---\n## Effect\nGallium is a fluid metal that responds to heat and magical input. It cannot form stable equipment but excels in reactive enchantment systems and arcane circuitry.\n\n---\n\n## Crafting Use\n- Arcane circuits\n- Enchantment matrices\n- Illusion-based devices\n- Alchemical systems\n\n---\n\n## Material Traits\n- Melts at low temperature  \n- Cannot form stable weapons or armor  \n- Highly responsive to magical input  \n\n---\n\n## Enchantment Use\n- Supports dynamic / shifting enchantments  \n- Useful in illusion and transformation systems  \n\n---\n\n## Combat Integration\n- Not usable for weapons or armor  \n\n---\n\n## Quote\n*\"It flows like thought — and changes just as easily.\"*"
