      "content": "---\ntags:\n  - Metal\nItem Class: Unusual\nMaterial Type: Metal\nMaterial Form: Ingot (Alloy)\nSource: Steel Ingot + Chromium Ingot\nWeight: 1.5kg\nWeight Class: Medium\nDurability: Very High\nEnchantment Affinity: 30% (+2 dice)\nDamage Modifier: 3\nArmor Modifier: 3\nMarket Value: 60 Marks\n---\n## Effect\nHigh Steel is an advanced alloy that combines the strength of Steel with the structural reinforcement of Chromium. It represents mastery of metallurgy and serves as the foundation for elite equipment.\n\n---\n\n## Alloy Composition\n- 1x [[Steel Ingot]]\n- 1x [[Chromium Ingot]]\n\n---\n\n## Enchantment Use\n- Supports mid-tier enchantments  \n- Highly stable under magical stress  \n- Ideal base for infusion and enhancement systems  \n\n---"
