      "content": "---\ntags:\n  - Metal\nItem Class: Unusual\nMaterial Type: Metal\nMaterial Form: Ingot\nSource: Thorium Ore\nWeight: 1.6kg\nWeight Class: Medium-Heavy\nDurability: Very High\nEnchantment Affinity: 45% (+3 dice)\nDamage Modifier: 3\nArmor Modifier: 3\nMarket Value: 70 Marks\n---\n## Effect\nThorium is a mana-charged metal that stores and releases energy. It enhances magical output while providing strong defensive properties.\n\n---\n\n## Crafting Use\n- Arcane armor\n- Energy weapons\n- Magical cores\n- Runic systems\n\n---\n\n## Material Traits\n- Stores residual magical energy  \n- Resistant to heat and arcane decay  \n- Requires careful handling due to instability  \n- Dense and highly durable  \n\n---\n\n## Enchantment Use\n- Enhances Radiant and Arcane effects  \n- Supports high-output enchantments  \n- Can store spell energy  \n\n---\n\n## Combat Integration\n- +3 Damage Modifier  \n- +3 Armor Modifier  \n- Favours magic-heavy builds  \n\n---\n\n## Crafting Source\n- Requires: 4x [[Thorium Ore]]\n\n---\n\n## Quote\n*\"Power given form — and barely contained.\"*"
