      "content": "---\ntags:\n  - Metal\nItem Class: Common\nMaterial Type: Metal\nMaterial Form: Ingot\nSource: Zinc Ore\nWeight: 0.9kg\nWeight Class: Light\nDurability: Low\nEnchantment Affinity: 10% (+0 dice)\nMarket Value: 6 Marks\n---\n\n\n## Effect\nZinc Ingots are rarely used alone but are critical in crafting alloys that require flexibility and responsiveness.\n\n---\n\n## Crafting Use\n- Alloy component\n- Artificer crafting\n- Mechanical parts\n\n---\n\n## Material Traits\n- Soft and reactive  \n- Low durability  \n- Enhances alloy flexibility  \n\n---\n\n## Alloy Use\n- [[Brass Ingot]]\n\n---\n\n## Enchantment Use\n- Improves energy responsiveness in alloys  \n- Helps distribute magical effects evenly  \n\n---\n\n## Crafting Source\n- Requires: 4x [[Zinc Ore]]\n\n---\n\n## Quote\n*\"The unseen force behind the perfect alloy.\"*"
