      "content": "---\ntags:\n  - Metal\nItem Class: Common\nMaterial Type: Metal\nMaterial Form: Ore\nRefines Into: Lead Ingot\nRefinement Ratio: 4:1\nWeight Class: Heavy\nDurability: Moderate\nEnchantment Affinity: 5% (+0 dice)\nMarket Value: 2 Marks\n---\n\n\n## Effect\nLead Ore absorbs magical energy, making it valuable for anti-magic crafting and containment.\n\n---\n\n## Lore\nCalled the *“Veil Stone,”* lead is said to silence magic itself.\n\n---\n\n## Material & Crafting Traits\n- Dense and heavy  \n- Toxic if mishandled  \n- Used in containment crafting  \n\n---\n\n## Refinement\n- Smelts into: [[Lead Ingot]]\n- Ratio: 4 Ore → 1 Ingot\n\n---\n\n## Alloy Use\n- Anti-magic alloys (future)\n\n---\n\n## Enchantment Use\n- Suppresses magic  \n- Blocks magical detection  \n\n---\n\n## Quote\n*\"Where magic ends, lead remains.\"*"
